latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
* Prevent Powershell-supported features from execution when Powershell blocked in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/153

#### Improvements
* Error logging for app when scan cannot be completed by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/158
* Source code review and hardening by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/541
* Move pdfs to sub-dir and cleanUp after. Remove unused imports by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/543
* New jsZip to zip files, proxy service to get proxy settings, resolve code 17 in getBrowserToRun by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/544
* Proxy Pac support, experimental flag disable file download by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/545
